Whenever I heard “from The Bronx” on WWE®, it stopped me in my tracks.

Because growing up, we didn’t always see people like us—on that kind of stage. 
 
So to chat with Damian Priest @archerofinfamy—WWE® Superstar and now a Bronx Walk of Fame inductee—and talk about what it means to rep the BX?

That’s full-circle. 
 
From mofongo to grit and dreams, Damian Priest reminds us: 
We’re not just built different—we’re built from community. 
 
And thanks to connections like @cricketwireless, moments like this get to live beyond the block. 
Because when you stay connected to your city, your story, and your people—anything’s possible.
